</a>

<!-- Image 3 -->
<a href="https://www.pexels.com/photo/black-and-green-toucan-on-tree-branch-17811/" target="_blank">
<img src="images/thumb3.jpg" alt="Image 3" width="100" height="100">
</a>

<!-- Add more images as needed -->
</div>

</body>
</html>
